              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35349362/" class="">第287页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46868435/" class=" " title="梦乃">梦乃</a>
                (上豆瓣，多读点书。。。。)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="35349362">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
